Joyce DiDonato en Bellas Artes</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/la-messa-in-si-minore-pappano-e-il-sacro-di-bach-allansc/" rel="next">La Messa in si minore: Pappano e il sacro di Bach all’ANSC <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 3 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-20614"> <article id="comment-20614" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8b6f6dd6f86d6af44cbe198b7da75237?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">zsazsa</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/fanoteatro-della-fortunarigoletto/#comment-20614"><time datetime="2014-03-01T20:09:13+00:00">1 marzo 2014 at 20:09</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>The  great Tenor, Gianluca Terranova is our Grand Hero!! We (I and my husband) adore his beautiful, thrilling voice, that noone else in the opera world! He has such a squillo, colourfulg and expressive timbre that noone else posess! And his charismatic stage presence is jus amazing! He is unique!</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-20652"> <article id="comment-20652" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/107cae3307cd133c6f5669ad18320214?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Simone</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/fanoteatro-della-fortunarigoletto/#comment-20652"><time datetime="2014-03-05T17:33:36+00:00">5 marzo 2014 at 17:33</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Solo una precisazione: anche per l&#8217;orchestra c&#8217;è stata una collaborazione. Non suonava solamente la &#8220;Rossini&#8221;, come si legge nella critica, ma suonavano la FORM (Fondazione Orchestra Regionale delle Marche) e la Osr (Orchestra Sinfonica Rossini) assieme.<br /> Vista la precisione riservata per il coro sarebbe opportuno fare lo stesso per l&#8217;orchestra.<br /> Grazie</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment byuser comment-author-admin even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-20657"> <article id="comment-20657" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/mia-foto-e1385566919652.jpg" width="1" height="1" alt="Giorgio Bagnoli" class="avatar avatar-75 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo" /></div><cite class="fn">Giorgio Bagnoli</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/fanoteatro-della-fortunarigoletto/#comment-20657"><time datetime="2014-03-06T10:28:36+00:00">6 marzo 2014 at 10:28</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>La ringrazio per la precisazione. Mi scuso per l&#8217;imprecisione.<br /> Abbiamo modificato la dicitura. Grazie ancora</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2014/03/fanoteatro-della-fortunarigoletto/#respond" style="disp